OL,4,Crepair worker suffered vibration injury
OL,6,FA council has been fined #60,000 after
OL,7,Fa pothole repair worker continued to
OL,8,Fuse power tools for 14 years despite
OL,9,Fdeveloping problems caused by
OL,10,Fvibrations.
OL,12,FSheffield Magistrates' Court heard the
OL,13,Femployee worked in the road
OL,14,Fmaintenance department at Rotherham
OL,15,FCouncil, carrying out tasks including
OL,16,Ffixing potholes.
OL,18,FDespite being diagnosed with hand arm
OL,19,Fvibration syndrome in April 2005, he
OL,20,Fcontinued to work with tools until
OL,21,F2019.
