OL,6,F"This was also not an isolated
OL,7,Fincident, with other staff working in
OL,8,Fthe council's road maintenance
OL,9,Fdivision also exposed to risks to
OL,10,Ftheir health, due to an unhealthy
OL,11,Fworking culture where these exposures
OL,12,Fare inadequately monitored."
OL,14,FProlonged and regular exposure to
OL,15,Fvibration can cause HAVS, which
OL,16,Fresults in painful and disabling
OL,17,Fdisorders of the nerves, blood supply,
OL,18,Fjoints and muscles of the hands and
OL,19,Farms.
