OL,3,CCouncil fined #60,000 after pothole
OL,4,Crepair worker suffered vibration injury
OL,6,FInvestigators found that
OL,7,Frecommendations to limit the man's
OL,8,Fexposure to vibrating tools were
OL,9,Fignored.
OL,11,FThey also found workers were
OL,12,Fincentivised to continue using
OL,13,Fvibrating tools through a bonus scheme
OL,14,Fand overtime payments.
OL,16,FWorkers were allowed to work up to the
OL,17,Frecommended exposure limit and were
OL,18,Fonly moved to other tasks when their
OL,19,Fhealth deteriorated.
